\f0\b\fs40 \cf2 1. Introduction\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa400\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \cf2 Welcome to 
\f0\b \cf2 Tutor Polly
\f1\b0 \cf2 ! This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and disclose information when you use our iPhone application. By using our app, you agree to the terms outlined in this policy.\
